author: Ian S
comment: I liked IO 2015 wallpaper so much that it reminded me to look for it for 2016. I doubted it would exist as IO 2016 hasn't even happened yet. But, you surprised me! Thank you! Could I make one small request, though? The option to have a white background. And, if I were to be bold, a tiny weather icon and temperature would make me so happy. Other than that, I love the watch face. 😊
title: You made my day
